le</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">Analytics</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">tracking</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">script</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> ◯ </span><span class=\"mtk12\">Add</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">responsive</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">images</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> ◉ </span><span class=\"mtk12\">Add</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">an</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">automatic</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">sitemap</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> ◯ </span><span class=\"mtk12\">Generate</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">a</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">manifest</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">file</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> ◉ </span><span class=\"mtk12\">Add</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">Markdown</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">and</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">MDX</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">support</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> ◯ </span><span class=\"mtk12\">Add</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">Markdown</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">support</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> (</span><span class=\"mtk12\">without</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">MDX</span><span class=\"mtk1\">)</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>我選了 js (後面會提我把 js 轉成 ts 的過程)<br>\n樣式選擇 styled-components<br>\n沒有使用 CMS 而是直接用 md 檔， 所以加裝了 md/mdx support</p>\n<p>完成後 你的網站就可以跑起來了 ～<br>\n在 cmd 中 把本地端伺服器架起來<br>\n<code>npm run develop</code><br>\n然後開啟瀏覽器 輸入網址： <a href=\"http://localhost:8000\">http://localhost:8000</a><br>\n就可以看到你的網站了 🎉<br>\n之後就可以藉由編輯 src/pages/index.js 這個檔案<br>\n然後就可以馬上在畫面上看到更新<br>\n接著我會分享一些功能</p>\n<ul class=\"contains-task-list\">\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled> js to ts</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled> theme 暗黑模式</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled> i18n</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled> deploy to github-page</li>\n</ul>\n<p>以上是今天的分享 👋</p>\n<style class=\"grvsc-styles\">\n  .grvsc-container {\n    overflow: auto;\n    position: relative;\n    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;\n    padding-top: 1rem;\n    padding-top: var(--grvsc-padding-top, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    padding-bottom: 1rem;\n    padding-bottom: var(--grvsc-padding-bottom, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    border-radius: var(--grvsc-border-radius, 8px);\n    font-feature-settings: normal;\n    line-height: 1.4;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-code {\n    display: table;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line {\n    display: table-row;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n    width: 100%;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line > * {\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter-pad {\n    display: table-cell;\n    padding-left: 0.75rem;\n    padding-left: calc(var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem)) / 2);\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter {\n    display: table-cell;\n    -webkit-user-select: none;\n    -moz-user-select: none;\n    user-select: none;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter::before {\n    content: attr(data-content);\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-source {\n    display: table-cell;\n    padding-left: 1.5rem;\n    padding-left: var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem));\n    padding-right: 1.5rem;\n    padding-right: var(--grvsc-padding-right, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-source:empty::after {\n    content: ' ';\n    -webkit-user-select: none;\n    -moz-user-select: none;\n    user-select: none;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter + .grvsc-source {\n    padding-left: 0.75rem;\n    padding-left: calc(var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem)) / 2);\n  }\n  \n  /* Line transformer styles */\n  \n  .grvsc-has-line-highlighting > .grvsc-code > .grvsc-line::before {\n    content: ' ';\n    position: absolute;\n    width: 100%;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-diff-add::before {\n    background-color: var(--grvsc-line-diff-add-background-color, rgba(0, 255, 60, 0.2));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-diff-del::before {\n    background-color: var(--grvsc-line-diff-del-background-color, rgba(255, 0, 20, 0.2));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-number {\n    padding: 0 2px;\n    text-align: right;\n    opacity: 0.7;\n  }\n  \n  .dark-default-dark {\n    background-color: #1E1E1E;\n    color: #D4D4D4;\n  }\n  .dark-default-dark .mtk12 { color: #9CDCFE; }\n  .dark-default-dark .mtk1 { color: #D4D4D4; }\n  .dark-default-dark .mtk3 { color: #6A9955; }\n  .dark-default-dark .mtk11 { color: #DCDCAA; }\n  .dark-default-dark .mtk8 { color: #CE9178; }\n  .dark-default-dark .mtk14 { color: #F44747; }\n  .dark-default-dark .grvsc-line-highlighted::before {\n    background-color: var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-background-color, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1));\n    box-shadow: inset var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-border-width, 4px) 0 0 0 var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-border-color, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5));\n  }\n</style>"}},{"node":{"fields":{"name":"gatsby-blog"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Gatsby用起來_架起專案","date":"2022-09-13T04:42:09.509Z","image_cover":"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1615419235091-59bf9cbd530b?fit=crop&w=1000&q=100","type":"blog"},"html":"<h1>開始用 Gatsby 來架我的部落格</h1>\n<p>之前試著用 hexo 來架部落格<br>\n可以在短時間裡就把一個網站架好<br>\n真的是很快</p>\n<p>主題也有滿多可以在官網裡找<br>\n或者別人寫好的主題可以直接套來用<br>\n不過 有時候就是<br>\n覺得有些主題裡總是差了一點功能<br>\n但自己要調整的話 也是滿費勁的</p>\n<p>後來發現 Gatsby<br>\n覺得這套更有彈性<br>\n對我來說比較容易新增自己想要的功能<br>\n雖然彈性就代表著自己會花更多心力<br>\n不過我很享受 創造的過程</p>\n<p>雖然也有其他別的 React 相關框架可以當成部落格的<br>\n我想 next.js 或 remix.js<br>\n都可以很快地架出部落格 也有很多強大的功能<br>\n不過 覺得自己的部落格其實只需要靜態的呈現就足矣<br>\n所以就決定要使用 Gatsby 了！！</p>\n<p>之後會慢慢補一些在建立專案的時候 遇到的一些困難 😂<br>\n以上是今天的分享 👋</p>\n<style class=\"grvsc-styles\">\n  .grvsc-container {\n    overflow: auto;\n    position: relative;\n    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;\n    padding-top: 1rem;\n    padding-top: var(--grvsc-padding-top, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    padding-bottom: 1rem;\n    padding-bottom: var(--grvsc-padding-bottom, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    border-radius: var(--grvsc-border-radius, 8px);\n    font-feature-settings: normal;\n    line-height: 1.4;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-code {\n    display: table;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line {\n    display: table-row;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n    width: 100%;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line > * {\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter-pad {\n    display: table-cell;\n    padding-left: 0.75rem;\n    padding-left: calc(var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem)) / 2);\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter {\n    display: table-cell;\n    -webkit-user-select: none;\n    -moz-user-select: none;\n    user-select: none;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter::before {\n    content: attr(data-content);\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-source {\n    display: table-cell;\n    padding-left: 1.5rem;\n    padding-left: var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem));\n    padding-right: 1.5rem;\n    padding-right: var(--grvsc-padding-right, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-source:empty::after {\n    content: ' ';\n    -webkit-user-select: none;\n    -moz-user-select: none;\n    user-select: none;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter + .grvsc-source {\n    padding-left: 0.75rem;\n    padding-left: calc(var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem)) / 2);\n  }\n  \n  /* Line transformer styles */\n  \n  .grvsc-has-line-highlighting > .grvsc-code > .grvsc-line::before {\n    content: ' ';\n    position: absolute;\n    width: 100%;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-diff-add::before {\n    background-color: var(--grvsc-line-diff-add-background-color, rgba(0, 255, 60, 0.2));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-diff-del::before {\n    background-color: var(--grvsc-line-diff-del-background-color, rgba(255, 0, 20, 0.2));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-number {\n    padding: 0 2px;\n    text-align: right;\n    opacity: 0.7;\n  }\n  \n</style>"}}]}},"pageContext":{"language":"zh","i18n":{"language":"zh","languages":["en","zh"],"defaultLanguage":"en","generateDefaultLanguagePage":false,"routed":true,"originalPath":"/blog/","path":"zh/blog/"}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3764592887"]}